{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "17392761-c0a3-49c9-919a-7c8881ef791e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17392761-c0a3-49c9-919a-7c8881ef791e@1.pkg/1772597641962/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597642790", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17392761-c0a3-49c9-919a-7c8881ef791e@1.pkg/1772597641962/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597642790"}, "identifier": "17392761-c0a3-49c9-919a-7c8881ef791e", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>正确答案：B<strong>①③</strong>​<br />\n①&nbsp;<strong>正确</strong>&nbsp;—— 遵守社会规范、具备同理心是社会适应能力的重要表现。<br />\n②&nbsp;<strong>无关</strong>&nbsp;—— 成绩和获奖属于学业能力，不直接体现社会适应能力。<br />\n③&nbsp;<strong>正确</strong>&nbsp;—— 善于沟通合作、主动承担责任是良好社会适应能力的体现。<br />\n④&nbsp;<strong>无关</strong>&nbsp;—— 精通网络游戏和网络社交属于虚拟技能，与社会适应能力无直接关系。</p>\n\n<p>因此，符合题意的选项是&nbsp;<strong>①③</strong>，即&nbsp;<strong>B</strong>。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）社会适应能力是指个体在社会生活中有效应对各种情境的综合素质。下列属于良好社会适应能力表现的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①遵守社会规范，具备同理心</p>\n\n<p>②成绩优异，获得各类奖项</p>\n\n<p>③善于沟通合作，主动承担责任</p>\n\n<p>④精通网络游戏，擅长网络社交</p>\n", "title": "（改编）社会适应能力是指个体在社会生活中有效应对各种情境的综合素质。下列属于良好社会适应能力表现的是（   ）①遵守社会规范，具备同理心②成绩优异，获得各类奖项③善于沟通合作，主动承担责任④精通网络游戏，擅长网络社交", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/17392761-c0a3-49c9-919a-7c8